Per-card row template for `ChapterCards`. Receives projected subobject
values as named args via SMW's `format=template | named args=yes`. The
leading newline inside `<includeonly>` is load-bearing — SMW
concatenates row-template invocations with no separator, and MediaWiki's
block-level `<div>` parser needs each card to start at line-start.
</noinclude>
